"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-rafael-nadal-serena-williams-help-light-cauldron-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony for the 2024 Paris Olympics was full of memorable and astonishing scenes as France put on quite a show on the Seine River.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9688672737728369, \"rank\": 0.02377088561364715, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just when fans thought the Olympics were about to officially commence, some special guests popped up to transfer the Olympic Flame along the Seine River: Spanish tennis star Rafael Nadal and American tennis legend Serena Williams.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans could not believe that two of the most famous tennis players of all time were included in this iconic moment, especially since both Nadal and Williams are not French.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999257652262, \"rank\": 7.423487641839956e-08, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other athletes highlighted in the passing of the Olympic Flame seemed to all be notable French athletes.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.790542522921942, \"rank\": 0.26221130839249607, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}